txt.en: You have finished distributing medical supplies among the Dâr Tabib healers.
Chakâr has asked you to deliver medical supplies to healers in and around Dâr Tabib.\n\nDâr Tabib is located in the south-west area of the Tor-gardens.
You have finished distributing medical supplies among the Dâr Tabib healers, and in the process, alleviated some of their stress.
'Just as I ran out! What a relief.'
'You have my gratitude -- and our patients', of course.'
'I have some fresh medical supplies that need to be distributed among the healers in and around the building.\n\n'Could you assist me with this task? I would be happy to pay you in advance.'
Aiding the Healers of Dâr Tabib
The healers of Dâr Tabib await fresh medical supplies.
